  HorizontalAlignment: Center
  MeshShadowMode: None
  ShadowColor: {x: 1.000000, y: 1.000000, z: 1.000000, w: 1.000000}
  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    In this minimal Connected Lenses example, a prefab is instantiated and can be manipulated by both players in the Lens.
    
    Build and run the Lens on two devices, then start it in Multiplayer mode. Look at each other to synchronize your positions.
    
    A ghost model will appear between you and the other player. Take turns manipulating the scene object to see how changes are shared.
